thinking
I'm thinking about adding helper functions after the `getServerProviderPreference` function. It makes sense to include these additional functions right there since it could streamline the process and enhance usability. However, I want to ensure their integration doesn't complicate the existing code. I'm curious about how many helpers would be beneficial and which specific functionalities would provide the most value to users. I guess a careful balance is necessary!
